{"tid":675911,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"兩匪闖海港城太子珠寶　1分鐘掠500萬鑽飾 20顧客職員尖叫逃出","createTime":"2018-05-24T02:51:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T05:28:36.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"2973bc307362a19d06f8f683014e04c33c76aaed","tid":675911,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:51:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399904\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399904&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh8mB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=d48afbde\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180524%2F20399904&h=5b7f5a6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180524/20399904</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年05月24日 <br />\n<br />\n兩匪闖海港城太子珠寶　1分鐘掠500萬鑽飾<br />\n20顧客職員尖叫逃出<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24la8p11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24la8p11.jpg&h=61de38f1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■賊匪撬爆飾櫃玻璃，掠去總值約500萬元珠寶鑽飾。溫文學攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】兩名賊匪昨晚闖入尖沙嘴海港城的太子珠寶鐘錶行，以利刀指嚇職員並撬爆飾櫃玻璃，一分鐘內掠去數枚總值約500萬元的珠寶鑽飾後奪門逃去。大批警員手持盾牌警棍，在附近進行大搜捕，但未有所獲。太子珠寶鐘錶主席鄧鉅明對事件表示無奈，「職員畀刀指住咗，成個過程只有1分鐘，都做唔到啲咩，最緊要佢哋冇事。」<br />\n<br />\n記者：馬耀文　溫文學<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現場為海港城3樓的太子珠寶鐘錶，消息指兩名賊匪戴帽及口罩。昨晚7時許，兩匪闖進珠寶店，一匪拔出利刀指嚇職員揚言打劫，並以廣東話大叫職員「咪郁」，另一匪用鐵筆撬開近門口的飾櫃玻璃，搶去6枚珠寶鑽飾，包括兩條頸鏈、一隻手鈪及兩隻戒指等，得手後衝出門口逃走。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a0801a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa0801a.gif&h=132b766d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■地上為被撬爆的飾櫃玻璃（虛線示）。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24la8p98.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24la8p98.jpg&h=c54981c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■女幫辦在現場調查。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/a0801b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2Fa0801b.gif&h=9da4718e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n警方搜捕　氣氛緊張<br />\n<br />\n據目擊者稱，當時聽到店內傳出尖叫聲，跟着便有最少20名相信是職員及客人的男女走出店外躲避，未幾「店內再傳嚟爆玻璃聲，之後有兩個人衝出珠寶店，沿扶手電梯跑落下層。」目擊者指其中一名賊人戴漁夫帽，身穿深色衫。<br />\n<br />\n警方接報趕至，大批警員手持盾牌展開搜捕，並封鎖珠寶店及賊人用作逃走的扶手電梯調查。現場所見，廣東道海港城至中港城一段泊滿警車，警員大舉搜捕賊人，氣氛緊張。警員並翻查閉路電視片段追緝賊人，據稱，警方其後在海防道天橋底一個垃圾箱內，撿獲一個口罩，懷疑是匪徒棄下，珠寶店職員點算後，損失約500萬元珠寶。<br />\n<br />\n太子珠寶鐘錶由商人鄧鉅明於1984年創立，現時全港共有18間分店。人稱「太子鄧」的鄧鉅明，亦是港大基金的名譽會長。他事後回覆《蘋果》查詢時表示，劫案中被扑爆的是珠寶櫃，賊人掠去戒指、頸鏈等首飾。鄧鉅明表示，由於被劫飾櫃對外，因此不會擺放太昂貴的珠寶，但全屬新款。<br />\n<br />\n他又指店內所有飾櫃皆使用防爆玻璃，對於其珠寶店遇劫感到無奈，「職員畀刀指住咗，成個過程只有1分鐘，都做唔到啲咩，最緊要佢哋冇事。」<br />\n<br />\n去年9月尖沙嘴半年內發生兩宗珠寶店劫案，鄧鉅明在出席社交場合時曾回應稱，不用特別加強店舖保安，因店舖不會在櫥窗放太貴重的珠寶，雖然有防盜玻璃，但賊人都有方法破壞，惟有提醒員工小心。<br />\n<br />\n今次珠寶店遇劫後，他稱會加強店舖保安，例如提升閉路電視級數，以及於飾櫃加裝更多防盜鎖。  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n牙科助理認向14歲女露械<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n持刀漢東鐵車廂恐嚇乘客"},{"pid":"0ebf0561bede2bdfbdeb668ff70df97cb03f4911","tid":675911,"uid":111965,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"繼續輸入專才<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5264f2c3fb9a1e8b1e933cc200826387e1f09148","tid":675911,"uid":94871,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T02:55:07.000Z","msg":"係咪見個女幫辦幾好樣又影低左<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bd9b8cbf4c6ee8fd8d6db0f6d69f3c86213d9b56","tid":675911,"uid":54542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"牙科助理認向14歲女露械<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43aa25a6d53ecc5e8c969d9ddb90b6d18fe35ea0","tid":675911,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"打完劫都買唔起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b221c145f104213b08cb56a29e217d39af8012a4","tid":675911,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43aa25a6d53ecc5e8c969d9ddb90b6d18fe35ea0","tid":675911,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"打完劫都買唔起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:00:03.000Z","msg":"人地住公屋 扲500萬有排玩啦，人地為自己唔為下代<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e386131dfb63658db205a3cac2a4b6ec9bce82d","tid":675911,"uid":23236,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd9b8cbf4c6ee8fd8d6db0f6d69f3c86213d9b56","tid":675911,"uid":54542,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:52:39.000Z","msg":"牙科助理認向14歲女露械<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T04:14:06.000Z","msg":"扣你50分！"},{"pid":"6e080824ee7140dcd6c12df10476aceb6d22c030","tid":675911,"uid":170249,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T05:04:29.000Z","msg":"引入假難民 於香港犯案<br />\n<br />\n多謝晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e275e6c849952db30bc5681cc9e175c5cd2da7a3","tid":675911,"uid":60655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b221c145f104213b08cb56a29e217d39af8012a4","tid":675911,"uid":111996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43aa25a6d53ecc5e8c969d9ddb90b6d18fe35ea0","tid":675911,"uid":39381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:57:23.000Z","msg":"打完劫都買唔起樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}